<varlistentry><term><menuchoice>
<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></menuchoice></term>
<listitem><para><action>
Allows you to open new files for editing.  For Step by Step instructions see <link linkend="NewDoc">Beginning a New Document</link>.</action></para> <para>Typing 
<keycombo><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>
or clicking 
<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="filenew2.png" format="PNG" align="center"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>
 are equivilent to using the menubar. <anchor id="MenuOpen"/></para></listitem></varlistentry>

<varlistentry><term><menuchoice>
<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Open</guimenuitem></menuchoice></term>
<listitem><para><action>
For opening previously created KWord files.  For Step by Step instructions see <link linkend="Loading">Retrieving a Saved Document</link>.
</action></para> <para>Typing 
<keycombo><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>O</keycap></keycombo>
or clicking 
 <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="fileopen.png" format="PNG" align="center"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>
