Opens a window that lets you enter information related to the document (such as Authors name, Addresses, Phone numbers, Abstract, etc). This information is saved with the document for later classification.<anchor id="MenuClose"/>
</action></para> </listitem></varlistentry>

<varlistentry><term><menuchoice>
<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Close</guimenuitem></menuchoice></term>
