 are equivilent to using the menubar. <anchor id="MenuInsSC"/></para></listitem></varlistentry>

<varlistentry><term><menuchoice>
<guimenu>Insert</guimenu><guimenuitem>Special Character</guimenuitem></menuchoice></term>
<listitem><para><action>
Opens a dialog box which allows you to select characters not found on the keyboard.</action></para> <para>Typing 
<keycombo><keycap>Alt</keycap><keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>
